Type: Project
Package: atacseq.rnaseq.integration
Title: ATAC-seq and RNA-seq Integrative Analysis of TCGA-BLCA
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("User", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Integrative analysis of ATAC-seq chromatin accessibility and
    RNA-seq gene expression data comparing TCGA-BLCA (bladder cancer) cohorts
    against normal bladder (P0) controls. Includes differential accessibility
    and expression volcano plots, pi-score concordance analysis, Venn diagram
    overlap assessment, and Gene Ontology enrichment analysis.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
